    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/7d540e9942936dcf2b9ea4c8983c1f86.poster.avif?t=1761286657\" width=800 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/7d540e9942936dcf2b9ea4c8983c1f86.webm?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/7d540e9942936dcf2b9ea4c8983c1f86.mp4?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endure the harsh depths of Lightwood</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your destiny awaits for you! Discover the ancient mysteries behind the Kingdom's </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >decay as you meet all kinds of interesting insects and deadly foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/5fe9d2374d86a1ff7a0cc2f74924a116.poster.avif?t=1761286657\" width=800 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/5fe9d2374d86a1ff7a0cc2f74924a116.webm?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/5fe9d2374d86a1ff7a0cc2f74924a116.mp4?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore an ancient fallen kingdom inside a dying tree</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the wonderful and hunting insect kingdom awaiting for you in the <br>depths of Lightwood. There are secrets and mysteries behind every corner waiting for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/67067b7fbd22768bda781a270b23307d.poster.avif?t=1761286657\" width=800 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/67067b7fbd22768bda781a270b23307d.webm?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/67067b7fbd22768bda781a270b23307d.mp4?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master your skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every new area will be filled with multiple dangers to overcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knowledge over you skills will be key to progression and survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/2544826ee09579421d57635710ce24b2.poster.avif?t=1761286657\" width=800 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/2544826ee09579421d57635710ce24b2.webm?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/2544826ee09579421d57635710ce24b2.mp4?t=1761286657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A semi-open world Metroidvania</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Lightwood is meant to be explored however you<br>want, but you will have to earn that right! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well balanced and responsive combat made to provide a fluid experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new approach to the classical Metroidvania progression system.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A huge variety of enemies and bosses carefully created.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautifully crafted landscapes and music, made to enhance the overall game experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple purpose mechanics conceived to increase the player sense of mastery over the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join our Community</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow us on social media and discord to get more updates about the game!</p>",
